 * SLG47004V NVM Recovery v2 — Prime_Maxel-v3
 * 
 * Simplified: only tries known address pairs.
 * After erase, chips shifted from 0x08 to 0x00.
 * NVM space shifted from 0x09 to 0x01.
 * 
 * Strategy: write factory NVM via NVM address (0x01 or 0x09),
 * use register address (0x00 or 0x08) for erase commands.
 */

